angers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20crossed%20paths%20with%20many%20of%20the%20same%20faces%20during%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-saved-thousands-dollars-by-swapping-childcare-with-other-parents-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eday%20care%20drop-off%20and%20pick-up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20each%20day.%20I%20learned%20to%20treasure%20those%20micro%20conversations%20when%20checking%20our%20children%20in%20and%20out%2C%20grabbing%20car%20seats%2C%20and%20watching%20the%20teachers%20bring%20out%20their%20cute%20little%20fingerpaintings%20and%20art%20projects%20to%20take%20home.%20These%20moments%20created%20a%20bond%20between%20us%20despite%20us%20essentially%20being%20strangers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20day%20care%20had%20an%20indoor%20play%20space%20called%20The%20Treehouse%2C%20with%20after-hours%20events%20for%20parents%20and%20their%20kids.%20It%20created%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-pressure-to-have-more-mom-friends-is-stressful-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emeet%20other%20moms%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20while%20helping%20my%20children%20(then%20ages%201%20and%203)%20grow%20their%20social%20skills.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETuesday%20nights%20were%20our%20favorite.%20The%20theme%20was%20%26quot%3BWork%20It%20Out%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%245%20per%20kid%20covered%20two%20supervised%20hours%20of%20kid-play%20in%20The%20Treehouse%20while%20the%20moms%20got%20a%20full-body%20workout.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20became%20a%20weekly%20tradition%20for%20my%20crew%20and%20two%20other%20moms%2C%20Meredith%20and%20Christin%2C%20whose%20kids%20were%20the%20same%20ages%20as%20mine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-new-adult-friends-is-hard-app-helped-meet-people-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20start%20of%20new%20friendships%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20me%20and%20what%20has%20now%20become%20lifelong%20friendships%20for%20my%20children.%20My%20kids%20don't%20remember%20a%20time%20when%20they%20weren't%20friends%20with%20the%20other%20Treehouse%20kids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ec10d70-4d48-4bb0-82a6-fc2bf255c7d1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESharing%20the%20good%2C%20bad%2C%20and%20insanity%20of%20motherhood%2C%20and%20more%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20The%20Treehouse%20ended%20its%20after-hours%20events%2C%20our%20trio%20continued%20the%20Tuesday%20tradition%2C%20hosting%20Work%20It%20Out%20at%20each%20other's%20houses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20Tuesdays%20evolved%20into%20lunch%20dates%2C%20park%20trips%2C%20weekend%20play%20dates%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-doesnt-do-birthday-parties-after-first-year-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebirthday%20celebrations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20a%20three-way%20text%20thread.%20We%20socialized%20often%2C%20with%20and%20without%20our%20kids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeredith%20and%20I%20surprised%20our%20kids%20by%20meeting%20up%20at%20Dollywood%20one%20summer%20day%20and%20again%20at%20Six%20Flags%20several%20years%20later.%20We%20have%20a%20long-standing%20tradition%20of%20going%20river%20tubing%20each%20summer%20right%20before%20the%20new%20school%20year%20starts.%20We%20gave%20Christin%20a%20baby%20shower%20and%20a%20meal%20train%20to%20welcome%20her%20second%20daughter.%20She's%20my%20go-to%20when%20I%20need%20help%20with%20school%20transportation.%20And%20since%20our%20older%20boys'%20birthdays%20are%20just%20three%20days%20apart%2C%20we%20plan%20their%20parties%20around%20each%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristin%20keeps%20an%20eye%20on%20my%20house%20when%20I'm%20out%20of%20town%2C%20feeds%20my%20pets%2C%20and%20gives%20me%20a%20voice%20of%20reason.%20She's%20lived%20in%20our%20town%20much%20longer%20than%20I%20have%20and%20knows%20everyone%20and%20everything%20that%20happens%2C%20which%20is%20why%20she's%20the%20first%20person%20I%20go%20to%20when%20I%20have%20questions.%20She's%20been%20a%20voice%20of%20reason%20for%20me%20more%20times%20than%20I%20can%20count.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20more%20time%20we%20spent%20together%2C%20the%20easier%20it%20was%20for%20me%20to%20befriend%20other%20moms.%20Lauren%2C%20Aundrea%2C%20and%20Quintina%20became%20familiar%20faces%20at%20birthday%20parties%2C%20park%20dates%2C%20and%20play%20dates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20children%20have%20formed%20inseparable%20bonds%20because%20they%20see%20each%20other%20often%20in%20and%20out%20of%20daycare.%20Even%20though%20they've%20made%20new%20friends%20over%20the%20years%2C%20they're%20still%20closest%20to%20the%20ones%20from%20their%20pre-school%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22908c3011-b490-44f2-9376-76c93f0ee53b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFamily%20is%20also%20the%20people%20you%20choose%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20text%20thread%20is%20now%20an%20eight-person%20collaboration%2C%20and%20it%20grows%20ever%20longer.%20And%20to%20think%20I%20almost%20didn't%20choose%20day%20care.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe're%20long%20removed%20from%20Tuesdays%2C%20The%20Treehouse%2C%20and%20day%20care%2C%20and%20life%20has%20gotten%20busy%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20Most%20of%20our%20kids%20play%20sports%20or%20take%20lessons%20of%20some%20sort.%20One%20of%20our%20friends%20moved%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20away.%20Another%20is%20going%20through%20cancer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20distance%2C%20schedules%2C%20and%20life's%20unexpected%20surprises%20can't%20divide%20us.%20We%20still%20trick-or-treat%20together%2C%20do%20craft%20nights%2C%20celebrate%20birthdays%20(and%20know%20when%20each%20kid's%20birthday%20is%20coming%20up)%2C%20discuss%20school%20and%20sports%2C%20and%20plan%20outings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20kids%20brought%20us%20together%2C%20but%20we%20chose%20to%20become%20friends.%20Now%2C%20more%20than%20eight%20years%20later%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20choose%20friendship%20despite%20the%20different%20roads%20we've%20traveled.%20We%20might%20go%20longer%20between%20visits%20or%20texts%2C%20but%20we%20always%20know%20where%20to%20turn%20when%20one%20of%20us%20needs%20help%2C%20advice%2C%20an%20answer%2C%20or%20just%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmet-my-group-of-friends-through-my-kids-day-care-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743279841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e3113469253ccddf9a4683%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmet-my-group-of-friends-through-my-kids-day-care-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20almost%20didn't%20send%20my%20kids%20to%20day%20care%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20I%20did.%20Through%20it%20I%20met%20my%20core%20group%20of%20friends%20who%20are%20like%20family%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alli%20Hill)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmet-my-group-of-friends-through-my-kids-day-care-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sedition%20case%20against%20Hasina%2C%2072%20others%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743279715000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119726147%2Cimgsize-40042.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsedition-case-against-hasina-72-others%2Farticleshow%2F119726127.cm