202000-batch%20IAS%20officer.%20She%20also%20has%20a%20Masters%20degree%20in%20International%20Politics%20from%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%20She%20is%20also%20a%20gold%20medallist%20in%20the%20IAS%20Academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Karthikeyan%20served%20as%20a%20collector%20in%20Maoist-affected%20Sundargarh%20district.%20She%20is%20known%20to%20have%20started%20the%20cycle%20scheme%20for%20highschool%20students%20through%20sponsorships%20offered%20through%20a%20bank%2C%20under%20the%20motto%2C%20%26quot%3BMobility%20is%20Empowerment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20that%20improved%20the%20enrolment%20of%20girls%20in%20schools%20was%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20state%20government%20for%20all%20schools%20across%20Odisha.%20She%20is%20known%20to%20have%20used%20sports%20such%20as%20football%20to%20wean%20away%20young%20people%20from%20Maoist%20influence%20in%20violence-prone%20districts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20and%20later%20setting%20up%20hostels%20for%20girls%20and%20boys%20interested%20in%20pursuing%20hockey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20she%20introduced%20eggs%20in%20the%20midday%20meals%20scheme%20in%20all%20government%20schools%20of%20Sundergarh.%20Inaugurated%20by%20Mr%20Patnaik%2C%20this%20too%20was%20later%20scaled%20up%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fqgj500p_sujata-r-karthikeyan-bill-clinton_625x300_29_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Karthikeyan%20was%20the%20first%20woman%20collector%20of%20Cuttack%20district.%20She%20then%20joined%20as%20Director%20of%20Social%20Welfare%20in%20the%20state%20government.%20She%20steered%20the%20flagship%20initiative%20of%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20'Mission%20Shakti'%20for%20years%2C%20connecting%2070%20lakh%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentred%20around%20credit%20linkages%20to%20women-run%20self-help%20groups%20(SHGs)%2C%20this%20scheme%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20pushed%20women's%20enterprises%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20thrust%20of%20Mission%20Shakti%20was%20identity%20and%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20SHG%20members%20were%20routinely%20taken%20on%20exposure%20visits%20to%20Dubai%20and%20Singapore.%20To%20encourage%20marketing%20of%20SHG%20products%2C%20'Mission%20Shakti'%20bazaars%20were%20set%20up%20across%20Odisha.%20An%20iconic%20boutique%20store%20was%20also%20set%20up%20in%20Bhubaneswar.%20This%20scheme%20came%20under%20the%20spotlight%20when%20Microsoft%20founder%20Bill%20Gates%20visited%20one%20of%20the%20stores%20and%20appreciated%20the%20marketing%20of%20agricultural%20products%20to%20an%20urban%20consumer%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Karthikeyan%20also%20served%20as%20Culture%20Secretary%2C%20a%20post%20she%20held%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20of%20five%20months.%20It%20was%20during%20her%20time%20in%20office%20that%20the%20state%20hosted%20the%20first%20world%20Odia%20language%20conference%20in%20Bhubaneswar.%20It%20was%20attended%20by%20language%20enthusiasts%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%20Odia%20diaspora%20and%20thousands%20of%20college%20students%20and%20was%20a%20big%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20election%20last%20year%2C%20Ms%20Karthikeyan%20was%20transferred%20to%20a%20less%20influential%20post%20following%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC).%20The%20transfer%20was%20initiated%20after%20the%20BJP%20filed%20a%20complaint%20accusing%20her%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3BBJD%20agent%26quot%3B.%20The%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20defeating%20the%20BJD%20that%20had%20governed%20the%20state%20for%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Mr%20Pandian%20quit%20active%20politics.%20Ms%20Karthikeyan%20first%20took%20child%20care%20leave%20for%20six%20months%2C%20and%20rejoined%20duty%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%20after%20the%20state%20government%20run%20by%20the%20BJP%20declined%20her%20application%20to%20extend%20her%20leave%20by%20six%20more%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20serving%20as%20the%20special%20secretary%20in%20the%20state%20finance%20department%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743259320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F521gdh5_sujata-r-karthikeyan_625x300_29_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-approves-odisha-ias-officer-sujata-karthikeyan-request-for-voluntary-retirement-8041156%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20approved%20Odisha%20cadre%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20Sujata%20R%20Karthikeyan's%20request%20to%20be%20relieved%20from%20service.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20third%20most%20dangerous%20country%20to%20drive%2C%20Norway%20safest%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743258912000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-third-most-dangerous-country-to-drive-norway-safest-report-125032900663_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%2C%20at%2049th%20place%2C%20was%20listed%20among%20the%20bottom%20five%20with%20the%20US%20ranking%2051%2C%20making%20it%20the%20third%20most%20dangerous%20country%20to%20drive%2C%20according%20to%20Zutobi.com%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-third-most-dangerous-country-to-drive-norway-safest-report-125032900663_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Genelia%20reveals%20she%20was%20discouraged%20from%20making%20a%20comeback%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743258739000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119713740%2Cimgsize-54220.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fgenelia-dsouza-reveals-she-was-discouraged-from-making-a-comeback-after-a-decade-long-sabbatical-i-remember-riteish-deshmukh-telling-me-%2Farticleshow%2F119713657.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119713657.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EGenelia%20D'Souza%20made%20a%20triumphant%20return%20to%20acting%20with%20her%20Marathi%20debut%20film%20Ved%2C%20alongside%20her%20husband%2C%20Riteish%20Deshmukh.%20The%20film%20became%20a%20massive%20success%2C%20emerging%20as%20the%20second-highest-grossing%20Marathi%20film%20after%20Sairat.%20However%2C%20the%20journey%20back%20to%20the%20screen%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%20for%20the%20actor%2C%20who%20recently%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20discouraged%20from%20making%20a%20comeback%20after%20a%20decade-long%20sabbatical.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fgenelia-dsouza-reveals-she-was-discouraged-from-making-a-comeback-after-a-decade-long-sabbatical-i-remember-riteish-deshmukh-telling-me-%2Farticleshow%2F119713657.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Trump's%20Tariff%20War%20Could%20Leave%20Millions%20Of%20Americans%20Without%20Toilet%20Paper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20proposed%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%20could%20trigger%20an%20unexpected%20crisis%20in%20America%2C%20leading%20to%20panic-buying%20seen%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic.%20The%20Trump%20administration's%20plan%20to%20almost%20double%20duties%20on%20Canadian%20softwood%20lumber%20could%20disrupt%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20something%20nobody%20wants%20to%20be%20caught%20without--%20toilet%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20promised%20to%20hike%20duties%20on%20softwood%20lumber%20to%2027%20per%20cent%20as%20soon%20as%20April%202%2C%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20additional%20levies%20pushing%20the%20rate%20to%20more%20than%2050%20per%20cent.%20The%20move%20could%20hit%20the%20availability%20of%20northern%20bleached%20softwood%20kraft%20pulp%20(NBSK)%2C%20a%20material%20derived%20from%20wood%20chips%20that%20is%20used%20to%20make%20toilet%20paper%20and%20paper%20towels%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Bloomberg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENBSK%20is%20prized%20for%20its%20tensile%20strength%20and%20constitutes%20about%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20standard%20US%20bathroom%20tissue%20and%20half%20of%20a%20typical%20paper%20towel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20US%20imported%202%20million%20tons%20of%20Canadian%20NBSK%2C%20Brian%20McClay%2C%20chairman%20of%20Trusted%20Providers%20of%20Global%20Pulp%20Market%20Information%2C%20told%20Bloomberg%2C%20highlighting%20the%20longstanding%20reliance%20of%20American%20paper-goods%20producers%20on%20Canadian%20pulp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20these%20mills%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20some%20of%20the%20big%20branded%20products%2C%20not%20only%20want%20softwood%20pulp%20from%20Canada%2C%20they%20want%20softwood%20pulp%20from%20this%20particular%20mill%20-%20they've%20been%20using%20it%20for%2030%20years%20and%20they%20will%20not%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20McClay%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Canadian%20pulp%20mills%20close%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20fiber%20supply%2C%20I%20can't%20think%20of%20any%20other%20option%20for%20them%20-%20they%20just%20can't%20switch%20the%20recipe%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcClay%20warned%20that%20if%20import%20taxes%20on%20lumber%20exceed%2050%25%2C%20as%20they're%20currently%20on%20track%20to%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20going%20to%20put%20some%20sawmills%20out%20of%20business%2C%20and%20that'll%20reduce%20the%20supply%20of%20wood%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20don't%20really%20cut%20trees%20for%20making%20pulp%20in%20Canada%2C%20we%20depend%20on%20residual%20chips%20from%20sawmills.%20It%20would%20certainly%20boost%20the%20cost%20and%20probably%20reduce%20output%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EReminder%20Of%20Pandemic%20Panic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scenario%20risks%20reviving%20painful%20memories%20of%20pandemic-era%20toilet%20paper%20shortages%2C%20when%20store%20shelves%20were%20stripped%20bare%20amid%20panic%20buying.%20Another%20possibility%20of%20the%20scenario%20could%20be%20higher%20prices%20at%20the%20checkout%20counter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Americans%20Want%20Canadian%20Lumber%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20long%20promoted%20tariffs%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20bring%20manufacturing%20back%20to%20the%20US%2C%20and%20he's%20repeatedly%20said%20his%20country%20doesn't%20need%20Canadian%20lumber.%20But%20that%20stance%20doesn't%20account%20for%20the%20specific%20qualities%20of%20Canadian%20softwood%20pulp%2C%20which%20industry%20executives%20say%20can't%20be%20easily%20substituted%20with%20American%20alternatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Frederic%20Verreault%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20corporate%20affairs%20at%20Les%20Chantiers%20de%20Chibougamau%20Ltee%2C%20a%20Quebec%20wood%20processor%2C%20Americans%20buy%20Canadian%20products%20because%20%26quot%3Bthey%20are%20the%20best%20and%20the%20most%20integrated%20into%20their%20factories.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESawmills%20are%20difficult%20to%20adjust%2C%20so%20they%20typically%20run%20either%20full%20tilt%20or%20not%20at%20all%2C%20Jean-Francois%20Samray%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Quebec%20Forest%20Industry%20Council%2C%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20pipelines%2C%20it's%20like%20power%20grids%3A%20It's%20all%20full%2C%20or%20all%20empty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20softwood%20industry%20operates%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bpure%20and%20perfect%20competition%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20in%20a%20market%20like%20that%2C%20there%20will%20be%20temporary%20closures%2C%20reduced%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20will%20have%20an%20%26quot%3Beffect%20on%20continental%20supply%20and%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20Tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20long-running%20trade%20dispute%2C%20the%20US%20currently%20applies%20duties%20totaling%20more%20than%2014%20per%20cent%20on%20Canadian%20lumber.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20set%20to%20increase%20this%20year%2C%20taking%20the%20cumulative%20burden%20to%20almost%2027%20per%20cent%2C%20according%20to%20a%20US%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20proposal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House's%20threatened%2025%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20on%20many%20Canadian%20goods%20would%20mean%20import%20taxes%20totaling%20about%2052%20per%20cent.%20And%20that's%20before%20the%20conclusion%20of%20a%20Trump-ordered%20investigation%20into%20national%20security%20concerns%20around%20lumber%20imports%2C%20which%20could%20mean%20even%20more%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%202%2C%20a%20US%20delay%20in%20applying%20the%2025%20per%20cent%20levies%20to%20goods%20covered%20under%20its%20trade%20deal%20with%20Canada%20is%20due%20to%20expire.%20The%20same%20day%2C%20Trump%20has%20pledged%20to%20unveil%20additional%20sweeping%20tariffs%20to%20make%20US%20trade%20with%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20%26quot%3Breciprocal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743258720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-06%2Fandt6co4_australia-toilet-paper-buying-afp_625x300_26_June_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv