%22%3A%22Pete%20Hegseth%20signs%20memo%20to%20shrink%20Defense%20Department's%20workforce%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20boost%20efficiency%20and%20'incentivize%20top%20performers'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22967%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%20signs%20a%20memorandum%20aboard%20an%20aircraft%20over%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20March%2028%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e7f6cb63d72727e198a372%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20Force%20Senior%20Airman%20Madelyn%20Keech%2C%20DOD%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDefense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%20signed%20a%20memo%20on%20Friday%20to%20reduce%20the%20DOD's%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20DOD%20will%20%26quot%3Brealign%20the%20size%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20civilian%20workforce%20and%20%26quot%3Bstrategically%20restructure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20department%20said%20in%20February%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20cut%20its%20civilian%20headcount%20by%205%20to%208%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-secdef-pete-hegseths-operator-casual-look-all-about-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDefense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20a%20memorandum%20on%20Friday%20that%20aims%20to%20shrink%20the%20Defense%20Department's%20civilian%20headcount%2C%20saying%20on%20X%20that%20it%20would%20help%20make%20the%20DOD%20%26quot%3Bmore%20efficient%20and%20incentivize%20top%20performers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%20DOD%20said%20the%20memo%20%E2%80%94%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BInitiating%20the%20Workforce%20Acceleration%20and%20Recapitalization%20Initiative%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20stated%20that%20the%20department%20would%20%26quot%3Brealign%20the%20size%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20civilian%20workforce%20and%20%26quot%3Bstrategically%20restructure%20it%20to%20supercharge%20our%20American%20warfighters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20net%20effect%20will%20be%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20number%20of%20civilian%20full-time%20equivalent%20positions%20and%20increased%20resources%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20we%20need%20them%20most%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said%2C%20per%20the%20DOD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20initiative%2C%20the%20department%20will%20embrace%20automation%20and%20seek%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20%26quot%3Bduplicative%20efforts%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bexcessive%26quot%3B%20bureaucracy%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20memo%2C%20Hegseth%20also%20called%20for%20the%20reopening%20of%20the%20deferred%20resignation%20program%2C%20which%20previously%20offered%20some%20full-time%20employees%20the%20chance%20to%20resign%20with%20full%20pay%20and%20benefits%2C%20and%20to%20offer%20voluntary%20early%20retirement%20to%20eligible%20civilian%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExemptions%20should%20be%20rare%2C%26quot%3B%20Hegseth%20said%20in%20the%20memo.%20%26quot%3BMy%20intent%20is%20to%20maximize%20participation%20so%20that%20we%20can%20minimize%20the%20number%20of%20involuntary%20actions%20that%20may%20be%20required%20to%20achieve%20the%20strategic%20objectives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20did%20not%20give%20a%20target%20percentage%20for%20layoffs.%20The%20DOD%2C%20which%20employs%20more%20than%20950%2C000%20civilians%20serving%20in%2094%20different%20countries%2C%20said%20in%20February%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20reduce%20its%20civilian%20workforce%20by%205%20to%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-agencies-musk-doge-targeted-list-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewider%20push%20to%20cut%20federal%20government%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%20spearheaded%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%20announced%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20following%20a%20DOGE%20review%2C%20the%20DOD%20would%20be%20terminating%20more%20than%20%24580%20million%20in%20programs%2C%20contracts%20and%20grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpete-hegseth-signs-memo-shrink-defense-department-workforce-cuts-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743254465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e7e03b69253ccddf9ab114%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpete-hegseth-signs-memo-shrink-defense-department-workforce-cuts-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20DOD%20will%20%26quot%3Brealign%20the%20size%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20civilian%20workforce%20and%20%26quot%3Bstrategically%20restructure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A190%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpete-hegseth-signs-memo-shrink-defense-department-workforce-cuts-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Carpenter's%20Daughter%20Tops%20Bihar%20Board%20Class%2010%20Exam%20With%2098%25%20Marks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETime%20and%20again%2C%20it%20has%20been%20proven%20that%20passion%20and%20determination%20can%20overcome%20any%20obstacle.%20Many%20students%20from%20financially%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%20achieve%20remarkable%20success%2C%20whether%20in%20board%20exams%20or%20the%20toughest%20competitive%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20a%20Bihar%20Board%20student%20once%20again%20demonstrated%20that%20sheer%20dedication%20and%20resilience%20can%20triumph%20over%20economic%20hardships.%20The%20state%20recorded%20three%20toppers%20in%20the%20Class%2010%20board%20exams%3A%20Sakshi%20Kumari%20from%20JP%20NS%20High%20School%20(Narhan)%20in%20Samastipu