id%3D%5C%2263ffcb25-c1eb-4fcd-9a2d-3edfb6ef837b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%20and%20durability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20West%20Elm%20Shelter%20Sleeper%20Sofa%20fully%20expanded.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e6dc5463d72727e1989169%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you're%20spending%20more%20than%20one%20night%20on%20this%20sofa%20bed%2C%20consider%20adding%20a%20mattress%20topper%20for%20a%20cozier%20surface.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shelter%20Sleeper%20Sofa%20looks%20just%20like%20its%20product%20photos%2C%20and%20overall%2C%20it's%20a%20comfortable%20option%20for%20both%20lounging%20and%20sleeping.%20The%20brand%20describes%20its%20cushions%20as%20a%202%20out%20of%205%20on%20the%20firmness%20scale%20(with%205%20being%20the%20firmest)%2C%20but%20personally%2C%20I%20think%20they're%20closer%20to%20a%203.%20They%20do%20have%20some%20give%2C%20but%20they're%20definitely%20not%20plush%20cushions%20that%20you'll%20sink%20into.%20Personally%2C%20I%20think%20that's%20a%20good%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20they%20don't%20show%20any%20signs%20of%20sagging%20after%20more%20than%20two%20years%20of%20use%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20might%20be%20too%20firm%20for%20your%20tastes%20if%20you%20like%20a%20cushy%2C%20sink-in%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sofa%20comes%20with%20four%20loose%20back%20cushions%20%E2%80%94%20two%20for%20the%20back%20of%20the%20sofa%20and%20two%20for%20the%20sides.%20They%20have%20a%20slight%20amount%20of%20give%20but%20hold%20their%20shape%20well.%20However%2C%20the%20Shelter%20Sofa%20does%20have%20a%20very%20low%20back%2C%20and%20some%20people%20may%20find%20that%20it%20doesn't%20offer%20enough%20support%20to%20comfortably%20sit%20upright%20for%20long%20periods.%20The%2024-inch%20seat%20depth%20is%20fairly%20average%2C%20making%20it%20comfortable%20for%20both%20sitting%20or%20lounging%2C%20and%20you%20can%20easily%20seat%20three%20people%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20opening%20a%20sofa%20Bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e6ecf069253ccddf9aa2ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20frame%20is%20heavy%20to%20lift%20initially%2C%20but%20lifts%20from%20a%20handle%20under%20the%20seat.%20%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20want%20to%20transform%20this%20sofa%20into%20a%20bed%2C%20you%20have%20to%20remove%20all%20its%20cushions%2C%20including%20the%20large%20bench%20seat%20cushion.%20I'll%20admit%20that%20it's%20a%20pain%20to%20find%20somewhere%20to%20store%20all%20the%20cushions%2C%20but%20this%20is%20a%20common%20issue%20with%20sofa%20beds.%20We%20usually%20end%20up%20just%20stacking%20them%20against%20a%20wall.%20From%20there%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20pulling%20the%20bed%20out%20using%20the%20handle%20under%20the%20seat.%20The%20frame%20is%20a%20bit%20heavy%2C%20so%20you%20do%20have%20to%20put%20your%20back%20into%20it%2C%20but%20once%20you%20get%20the%20first%20legs%20out%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20unfold%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20mattress.%20Once%20it's%20set%20up%2C%20I%20place%20the%20bench%20cushion%20vertically%20behind%20the%20mattress%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20cushy%20headboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20be%20honest%3A%20I've%20only%20personally%20slept%20on%20this%20sofa%20bed%20a%20few%20times%2C%20so%20I%20can't%20weigh%20in%20much%20on%20its%20comfort%20as%20a%20bed.%20Instead%2C%20I%20asked%20my%20brother%20and%20sister-in-law%20for%20their%20thoughts%2C%20as%20they%20generally%20sleep%20on%20it%20once%20a%20month.%20They%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20the%20most%20comfortable%20sleep%20surface%20in%20the%20world%20but%20is%20pretty%20standard%20of%20what%20they%20expect%20for%20a%20sofa%20bed.%20The%20memory%20foam%20mattress%20is%20fairly%20firm%20and%20droops%20slightly%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20so%20they%20usually%20use%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-topper%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emattress%20topper%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Ddadd3b219d21d4f37e981f5202a7d6fbcc0e7799871edeca31ebd151a8acfdf4%26postID%3D67e6c80213d2c9b73bbeb69c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fwest-elm-shelter-sleeper-sofa-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FMeliusly%2525C2%2525AE-Sleeper-Support-Board-48x60%252Fdp%252FB0BVWMSTL2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20board%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20they're%20staying%20for%20more%20than%20one%20night.%20With%20these%20added%20accessories%2C%20they%20said%20it's%20much%20more%20comfortable%2C%20and%20they're%20able%20to%20get%20a%20good%20night's%20rest%20on%20it.%20Keep%20in%20mind%2C%20these%20are%20extra%20bedding%20items%20you'll%20still%20need%20to%20find%20a%20place%20to%20store%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20mattress%20is%20fairly%20thin%2C%20it%20doesn't%20offer%20as%20much%20motion%20isolation%20as%20a%20standard%20mattress%2C%20and%20you'll%20definitely%20be%20able%20to%20feel%20a%20partner%20shifting%20around%20next%20to%20you%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20few.%20The%20good%20news%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20the%20metal%20frame%20offers%20solid%20support%2C%20so%20you%20can%20sit%20or%20lie%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20bed%20without%20worrying%20about%20it%20drooping.%20My%20brother%20tends%20to%20sleep%20warm%2C%20and%20he%20said%20that%20the%20mattress%20doesn't%20make%20him%20overheat%2C%20likely%20thanks%20to%20its%20gel-infused%20foam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e10e4c0-0d68-4bca-9b4e-1465a64ad9ba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20