0Elm%20Shelter%20Sleeper%20Sofa%20is%20a%20well-made%2C%20versatile%20piece%20of%20furniture.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20well-made%20and%20stylish%20piece%20of%20furniture%20for%20your%20living%20space%2C%20the%20West%20Elm%20Shelter%20Sleeper%20Sofa%20is%20a%20worthwhile%20option%20to%20consider.%20It's%20on%20the%20more%20expensive%20side%20%E2%80%94%20the%20price%20starts%20at%20%242%2C600%20and%20can%20go%20up%20to%20%243%2C100%20depending%20on%20the%20fabric%20you%20choose%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20made%20from%20high-quality%20materials%20and%20is%20more%20durable%20than%20cheaper%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%20of%20regular%20use%2C%20the%20sofa%20still%20looks%20as%20good%20as%20new%2C%20and%20we%20have%20overnight%20guests%20who%20sleep%20on%20it%20once%20a%20month%20(or%20sometimes%20more).%20They%20say%20its%20comfort%20level%20is%20fairly%20standard%20for%20a%20sofa%20bed%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20easily%20improved%20with%20accessories%20like%20a%20mattress%20topper%20and%2For%20support%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fwest-elm-shelter-sleeper-sofa-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743249601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e6dae1b8b41a9673fc05b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fwest-elm-shelter-sleeper-sofa-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20bought%20the%20West%20Elm%20Shelter%20Sleeper%20Sofa%20for%20when%20my%20family%20visits.%20After%20two%20years%2C%20it%20still%20looks%20like%20new%20and%20is%20comfy%20to%20sit%20and%20sleep%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jwong%40businessinsider.com%20(Camryn%20Rabideau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fg