g%20on%20the%20category.%20The%20revenue%20split%20was%20heavily%20skewed%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20couple%2C%20with%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20earnings%20retained%20by%20them%20and%20only%2025%20per%20cent%20shared%20with%20the%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20initially%20received%20payments%20from%20customers%20through%20cryptocurrencies.%20The%20ED%20has%20also%20discovered%20a%20bank%20account%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20where%20Rs%207%20crore%20had%20been%20transferred%20by%20Technius%20Limited.%20These%20funds%20were%20subsequently%20withdrawn%20in%20cash%20in%20India%20using%20international%20debit%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20probe%20agency%2C%20thousands%20of%20women%20may%20have%20been%20recruited%20through%20this%20racket.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743249000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ft0prkt8_noida-couple-porn-racket-_625x300_29_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnoida-couple-ran-onlyfans-like-op-probe-reveals-a-cyprus-connection-8040021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20couple%20in%20Noida%2C%20foreign%20funding%2C%20adult%20entertainment%20-%20a%20major%20online%20pornography%20racket%20was%20busted%2C%20uncovering%20an%20illegal%20network%20that%20stretched%20beyond%20international%20borders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnoida-couple-ran-onlyfans-like-op-probe-reveals-a-cyprus-connection-8040021%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20woman%20who%20lost%20130%20pounds%20shares%207%20changes%20she%20wasn't%20expecting%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20from%20people%20being%20nicer%20to%20her%20to%20food%20tasting%20different%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emma%20Roma%20Jayne%20in%20a%20green%20jumper%20in%20front%20of%20the%20sea%20and%20a%20sunset.%5C%22%20charse