reet%20her%20in%20the%20street%2C%20and%20strike%20up%20conversations%20with%20her%20now%2C%20whereas%20before%20she%20lost%20weight%20she%20felt%20%26quot%3Binvisible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b07c4b3f-6f25-4db5-b3ba-d56a8ed83705%5C%22%3EHer%20feet%20have%20gotten%20smaller%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20more%20random%20changes%20that%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20that%20was%20a%20thing%20is%20that%20my%20feet%20shrunk%2C%26quot%3B%20Roma%20Jayne%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20four%20pairs%20of%20shoes%2C%20all%20in%20different%20sizes%2C%20which%20she%20bought%20as%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funexpected-side-effects-from-weight-loss-reddit-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeet%20got%20smaller%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20she%20lost%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20feet%20are%20slimmer%20now%2C%20and%20she%20went%20from%20a%20US%20size%209%20shoe%20to%20a%207.5.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202014%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC5731565%2F%23sec8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20Turkish%20Journal%20of%20Surgery%20found%20that%2080%25%20of%20the%20212%20participants%2C%20who%20all%20underwent%20bariatric%20surgery%2C%20bought%20shoes%20at%20least%20one%20size%20smaller%20a%20year%20after%20the%20surgery.%20The%20researchers%20suggested%20this%20could%20be%20because%20of%20fat%20loss%20on%20the%20foot%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20arches%20getting%20higher%20once%20there%20is%20less%20weight%20pushing%20them%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220bc6c067-2204-4628-84a0-679039349911%5C%22%3EHer%20voice%20has%20changed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoma%20Jayne%20also%20said%20that%20her%20voice%20has%20gotten%20higher%20and%20sounds%20more%20clear%20since%20her%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20not%20much%20research%20on%20the%20impacts%20of%20weight%20loss%20on%20voice.%20A%20few%20small%2C%20limited%20studies%20have%20suggested%20that%20there%20could%20be%20minor%20changes%20to%20people's%20voices%20after%20bariatric%20surgery%2C%20but%20the%20differences%20aren't%20noticeable%20enough%20to%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22548%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mirror%20selfie%20of%20Emma%20Roma%20Jayne%20at%20the%20gym.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e3e7e7b8b41a9673fbb629%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22411%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoma%20Jayne%20works%20out%20regularly%20and%20eats%20healthily%20to%20maintain%20a%20lower%20weight%20after%20bariatric%20surgery.%3Cp%3EEmma%20Roma%20Jayne%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236769d9e-a0f4-4949-b4f0-c8adef0d061c%5C%22%3EHer%20skin%20is%20clearer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoma%20Jayne%20has%20previously%20struggled%20with%20acne%2C%20but%20found%20that%20her%20skin%20cleared%20up%20when%20she%20lost%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20she%20eats%20a%20low-carb%20diet%20and%20has%20cut%20out%20sugar.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aad.org%2Fpublic%2Fdiseases%2Facne%2Fcauses%2Fdiet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Academy%20of%20Dermatology%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eating%20high-glycemic%20foods%20that%20raise%20your%20blood%20sugar%20quickly%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20white%20bread%2C%20potato%20chips%2C%20pastries%2C%20and%20white%20rice%20%E2%80%94%20is%20associated%20with%20acne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoma%20Jayne%20also%20has%20PCOS%2C%20of%20which%20acne%20is%20a%20symptom.%20The%20UK's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fpolycystic-ovary-syndrome-pcos%2Ftreatment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Health%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20weight%20loss%20can%20improve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpcos-weight-loss-tips-why-it-can-be-harder-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esymptoms%20of%20PCOS%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6fae2c2-442b-4aa8-8ac9-bcfdc42af8c6%5C%22%3EHer%20tastes%20have%20changed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoma%20Jayne%20used%20to%20hate%20avocados%2C%20and%20now%20loves%20them.%20She%20also%20used%20to%20eat%20a%20lot%20of%20fruit%2C%20but%20now%20eats%20far%20less%20fruit%20and%20far%20more%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20systematic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10165840%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereview%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20research%2C%20published%20in%20the%20Nutrition%20Journal%20in%202023%2C%20found%20that%20across%2026%20studies%2C%20it%20seemed%20that%20weight%20gain%20and%20obesity%20could%20change%20people's%20perception%20of%20tastes%2C%20and%20increase%20their%20preferences%20for%20sweetness.%20However%2C%20the%20authors%20said%20that%20these%20results%20weren't%20conclusive%20and%20that%20more%20research%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emma%20Roma%20Jayne%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20in%20a%20gym.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e53aeeb8b41a9673fbd5b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoma%20Jayne%20has%20noticed%20changes%20other%20than%20weight%20loss%20after%20her%20bariatric%20surgery.%3Cp%3EEmma%20Roma%20Jayne%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0cecd73-c1c9-4a00-9066-28832d68d09e%5C%22%3EShe%20lost%20some%20friendships%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Roma%20Jayne%20lost%20weight%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20dealt%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20jealousy%20and%20resentment%20from%20friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20realized%20that%20they%20were%20my%20friends%20when%20I%20was%20bigger%20because%20I%20made%20them%20feel%20better%20about%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20that%20I'm%20on%20my%20own%20journey%20and%20bettering%20myself%20and%20making%20these%20healthy%20changes%2C%20suddenly%20they%20had%20a%20problem%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a88f3f8-ae2a-4e44-8dac-ffe0c9b91d96%5C%22%3EShe's%20more%20confident%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20bigger%2C%20I%20definitely%20used%20my%20size%20as%20a%20shield%20to%20protect%20myself%20from%20other%20people%20knowing%20the%20real%20me.%20Now%20that%20I%20feel%20so%20much%20more%20confident%20in%20myself%20and%20I%20have%20so%20much%20appreciation%20and%20love%20for%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Roma%20Jayne%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20the%20most%20confident%20version%20of%20myself%20that%20I've%20ever%20been%2C%20and%20I%20continue%20to%20get%20more%20and%20more%20confident%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20surrounding%20herself%20with%20the%20right%20people%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fbenefits-of-losing-weight%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimproved%20her%20confidence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbariatric-surgery-weight-loss-changes-unexpected-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743248161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e5847769253ccddf9a7c26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbariatric-surgery-weight-loss-changes-unexpected-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Emma%20Roma%20Jayne%20lost%20130%20pounds%20in%20two%20years%2C%20and%20says%20people%20treat%20her%20very%20differently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22skenny%40businessinsider.com%20(Serafina%20Kenny)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbariatric-surgery-weight-loss-changes-unexpected-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20you%20know%20Elon%20Musk%20o