%3Cp%3ESpecial%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20judge%20Alka%20Malik%20in%20her%20order%20acquitted%20Justice%20Yadav%20today.%20The%20final%20arguments%20in%20the%20case%20were%20heard%20in%20the%20court%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20filed%20the%20case%20against%20Justice%20Yadav%2C%20who%20had%20refuted%20the%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20committed%20any%20crime%2C%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20incriminating%20found%20during%20the%20entire%20trial%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20her%20final%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2013%2C%202008%2C%20a%20clerk%20at%20Justice%20Kaur's%20house%20in%20Chandigarh%20received%20a%20packet%20containing%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20cash.%20On%20discovering%20the%20mix-up%2C%20Justice%20Kaur%20immediately%20informed%20the%20then%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20and%20the%20Chandigarh%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20subsequently%20filed%20on%20August%2016%2C%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20took%20a%20significant%20turn%2010%20days%20later%20when%20the%20then%20administrator%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%2C%20General%20SF%20Rodrigues%20(retired)%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20filed%20a%20fresh%20FIR%20on%20August%2028%2C%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20investigation%2C%20the%20CBI%20found%20the%20cash%20was%20delivered%20by%20a%20clerk%20of%20former%20Haryana%20additional%20advocate%20general%20Sanjeev%20Bansal%2C%20who%20reportedly%20called%20Justice%20Kaur%20and%20said%20the%20money%20was%20meant%20for%20a%20certain%20%26quot%3BNirmal%20Singh%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20was%20mistakenly%20delivered%20to%20her%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202009%2C%20the%20CBI%20sought%20permission%20to%20prosecute%20Justice%20Yadav%2C%20which%20was%20granted%20by%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20in%20November%202