%20those%20names.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20materials%20and%20metals%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20that%20outperformed%20amid%20tariff%20volatility.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-record-rally-trump-tariffs-trade-war-uncertainty-investing-strategy-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGold%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20as%20investors%20run%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-inflation-high-stagflation-national-debt-investing-strategy-gold-energy-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafe-haven%20assets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Barbee%20thinks%20there's%20still%20more%20room%20for%20gold%20mining%20stock%20prices%20to%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211645b11-f49b-43c2-8d6b-916a2fd69729%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20things%20are%20out%20of%20your%20control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20best%20fund%20managers%20have%20bad%20days%20%E2%80%94%20or%20bad%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%202008%20was%20one%20of%20the%20roughest%20years%20in%20my%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbee%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20big%20drawdown.%20It%20was%2050%25%20or%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%20started%202009%20with%20another%2020%25%20decline.%20The%20especially%20frustrating%20part%20about%20the%20fund's%202008%20performance%20was%20that%20much%20of%20it%20was%20out%20of%20Barbee's%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20do%20your%20work%2C%20you%20can%20determine%20whether%20the%20company's%20on%20fiscally%20solid%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbee%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20suffered%20these%20big%20drawdowns%20anyway%20because%20it%20was%20much%20less%20about%20the%20companies%20themselves.%20It%20was%20much%20more%20about%20the%20other%20owners%20of%20the%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20homeowners%20began%20defaulting%20on%20their%20mortgages%2C%20highly%20levered%20banks%20like%20Lehman%20Brothers%20saw%20the%20value%20of%20their%20mortgage-backed%20securities%20plunge%20and%20experienced%20a%20credit%20crunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Lehman%20Brothers%20proprietary%20trading%20desk%20would%20own%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20names%20that%20they%20would%20then%20be%20forced%20to%20liquidate%20as%20they%20were%20getting%20the%20repo%20lines%20pulled%2C%20in%20what%20amounted%20to%20a%20huge%20margin%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbee%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20names%20traded%20down%20to%20underneath%20cash%20value%20per%20share.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20ride%20through%20periods%20of%20volatility%20where%20other%20stockholders%20might%20get%20washed%20out%20is%20a%20very%20important%20aspect%20of%20getting%20through%20those%20difficult%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbee%20added.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20the%20best%20opportunities%20become%20clearly%20available%20when%20you're%20feeling%20the%20worst%20about%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20staying%20steadfast%20paid%20off%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fund%20bounced%20back%20strong%20and%20was%20up%2091%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Barbee%2C%20the%20most%20rewarding%20part%20of%20the%20job%20has%20been%20the%20relationships%20he's%20built%20with%20clients.%20Some%20of%20his%20clients%20have%20been%20with%20him%20from%20the%20beginning%20and%20weathered%20the%20last%20two%20financial%20crises%20alongside%20the%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20have%20the%20clients%20that%20decide%20to%20stay%20with%20you%20through%20difficult%20times%2C%20and%20then%20have%20it%20work%20out%20for%20everybody%20is%20is%20a%20really%20rewarding%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdot-com-2008-crashes-recession-stock-market-tariffs-inflation-outperform-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%