%20the%20initiative%20taps%20into%20the%20entrepreneurial%20energies%20of%20local%20communities%2C%20empowering%20them%20to%20cater%20to%20both%20emerging%20and%20existing%20needs%20in%20rural%20economies.%20A%20key%20element%20in%20this%20ecosystem%20is%20the%20District%20Entrepreneurship%20Coalition%20(DEC)%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20enables%20collaboration%20among%20local%20stakeholders%20to%20co-create%20sustainable%20solutions.%20The%20DEC%20can%20be%20replicated%20across%20the%20country%2C%20driving%20scalable%20change%20while%20ensuring%20that%20these%20models%20are%20relevant%20for%20all%20sectors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20establish%20self-sustaining%2C%20aspiration-driven%20ecosystems%20where%20entrepreneurs%20thrive%20without%20needing%20continuous%20external%20intervention.%20The%20initiative%20goes%20beyond%20short-term%20support%20for%20entrepreneurs%20like%20Anita%E2%80%94it%20strives%20to%20build%20a%20self-sustaining%20ecosystem%20that%20drives%20long-term%20growth.%20At%20its%20core%20is%20the%20collective%20action%20for%20the%20development%20of%20non-traditional%20enterprises%20and%20systemic%20prototypes%2C%20designed%20to%20break%20barriers%20to%20entrepreneurship%20through%20collaboration%2C%20strategic%20partnerships%2C%20and%20a%20shared%20vision%20for%20inclusive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EScaling%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20so%20far%20is%20undeniable%2C%20but%20the%20vision%20is%20even%20bigger.%20By%202030%2C%20the%20programme%20aims%20to%20establish%201%2C00%2C000%20women-led%20enterprises%20and%201%2C000%20women-driven%20e-rickshaw%20services%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20creating%201%20million%20jobs%20in%20the%20process.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20realise%20this%20vision%2C%20the%20group%20has%20tied%20up%20with%20women%E2%80%99s%20institutions%20like%20SHGs%20(Self%20Help%20Groups)%20and%20CLFs%20(Cluster%20Level%20Federations)%20facilitated%20by%20SRLMs%